description: This file is the entry point for a React-based web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It then creates a React root and renders the App component within React.StrictMode into the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the specified DOM node.
